From b3eb82af47b109922fb5e21470b2d137048d3691 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Sudhanshu <sambastha@salesforce.com>
Date: Sun, 7 Jun 2026 23:45:41 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 4/4] feat(analytics): instrument booking funnel + payment
 (PR-5 of conversion-tracking)
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Wires Funnel D events end-to-end per plan.md §2.5/§2.6 and events.csv:

- SRP (PageSrp + TemplateSrp + MoleculeSRPCard): fires `search` on
  /srp entry with the latlng query, `view_search_results` once the SRP
  fetch resolves, batched `view_item_list` impressions through a new
  IntersectionObserver helper, and `select_item` on card click.
- New `src/lib/analytics/observer.js` factory (`createListImpressionTracker`)
  debounces card impressions ~1s and dedupes ids per session. SSR-safe
  no-op handle when `window`/`IntersectionObserver` is unavailable.
- Spot detail (PageSpotDetail): `view_item` after getSpotDetails resolves.
- Booking modal (OrganismBookingModal + TemplateSpotDetail): `begin_checkout`
  on open, `form_start` on first blur (gated), and the primary Ads
  conversion `generate_lead` for both auth (Rs 750, email/phone from
  user store, optional `transaction_id` from API booking id) and guest
  (Rs 500) paths. Email/phone go only inside `enhanced_conversion_data`
  so GTM hashes them client-side. Dedup keyed on lead_type+spot+id in
  `sessionStorage.parkspot_fired_leads` to defend against rapid double
  submits.
- Payment (PagePaymentGateway): `payment_initiated` after
  getBookingDetails validates the payment row, and `purchase` in the
  getStatus PAID branch with full enhanced_conversion_data. Dedup keyed
  on transaction_id (`?p=`) in `sessionStorage.parkspot_fired_purchases`
  so Cashfree retries / back-button revisits never double-count. Success
  redirect now carries `?from=booking&t=<paymentId>`.
- Thank-you (PageThankYou): fires `purchase_confirmed` when
  `?from=booking&t=<id>` is present (PR-4's vo|so|contact handling left
  for that PR's merge).
